Summary:
Water Sharer badge sharing system implemented with excellent security posture.
Zero critical/high vulnerabilities. Multi-layer validation, SQL injection prevention,
race condition protection via database constraints, comprehensive audit trail.

Key Features:
- Water Sharer badge allows holders to share with ONE other existing member
- Database constraints enforce business rules (one active grant, one-time receive)
- Cascade revocation maintains lineage integrity
- Audit logging for all badge operations
- Privacy-preserving implementation (no wallet exposure)

Security Highlights:
- Parameterized queries (SQL injection prevention)
- Authorization checks at multiple layers
- Transaction rollback on failure
- Comprehensive audit logging
- Privacy-preserving error messages

All acceptance criteria met. Ready for production deployment.
